Fully furnished, luxury 2 bedroom, 1 bathroom condo on the 20th floor in the Continental at Ballston building. Located in Arlington's Ballston/Virginia Square neighborhood, the property is close to restaurants and shopping. &nbsp;It offers easy access to the highway and metro into Washington or the VA suburbs. The Ballston Common mall, cinema, health club, street-level restaurants and retail stores is just a 6 minute walk.&nbsp;
The condo features a private balcony, kitchen stocked with all the tools needed for cooking, modern decor, a queen bed in the master and full bed in the 2nd bedroom. This property includes central air conditioning and&nbsp;in unit washer/dryer. The building offers a front desk staff during business hours, fitness center and attached parking garage. The Ballston Metro is just 1 block.&nbsp;Walk score: 89 (Very Walkable), transportation score: 70, and bike score: 80.&nbsp;
Please note: This property requires a 6 month minimum lease term.
